\c 4
\s UJesu ukhuluma lowesifazana weSamariya
\p
\v 1 Kwathi-ke iNkosi isisazi ukuthi abaFarisi sebezwile ukuthi uJesu wenza wabhabhathiza abafundi abanengi kuloJohane\x + 3.22,26.\x*,
\v 2 lanxa uJesu ngokwakhe wayengabhabhathizi, kodwa abafundi bakhe\x + 1 Kor. 1.14-17.\x*,
\v 3 wasuka eJudiya\x + 3.22. 7.1. 4.47,54.\x*, wasuka waya futhi eGalili\x + 2.11,12.\x*.
\p
\v 4 Kodwa kwakumele\x + Luka 17.11.\x* ukuthi adabule eSamariya\x + 1 Kho. 16.24.\x*.
\v 5 Wafika-ke emzini weSamariya okuthiwa yiSikari\x + Josh. 17.7. Seb. 7.16.\x*, eduze lesiqinti uJakobe asinika indodana yakhe uJosefa\x + Gen. 33.19. 48.22. Josh. 24.32. Joha. 4.12.\x*;
\v 6 lomthombo kaJakobe wawulapho. Ngakho uJesu ekhathele ngohambo\x + Luka 11.6.\x* wahlala ngokunjalo emthonjeni\x + 2 Kho. 7.7,10. Mark. 4.36.\x*. Kwakungaba lihola \w lesithupha\w**\x + 19.14. 1.39.\x*.
\v 7 Kwafika owesifazana evela eSamariya ukuzakukha amanzi; uJesu wathi kuye: Nginathisa.
\v 8 (Ngoba abafundi bakhe babehambile baya emzini, ukuze bathenge ukudla\x + 4.5,39.\x*.)
\v 9 Ngakho owesifazana umSamariya wathi kuye: Kungani wena ungumJuda ucela ukunatha kimi, owesifazana ongumSamariya? Ngoba amaJuda awalabudlelwano lamaSamariya\x + Luka 9.53. Mat. 10.5. Seb. 10.28.\x*.
\v 10 UJesu waphendula wathi kuye: Aluba ubusazi isipho sikaNkulunkulu, lokuthi ungubani othi kuwe: Nginathisa; ubuzacela kuye, njalo ubezakunika amanzi aphilayo\x + 7.38,39. Jer. 2.13. Zek. 14.8. Isa. 12.3. 44.3. Hez. 36.25. Zek. 13.1.\x*.
\v 11 Owesifazana wathi kuye: Nkosi, kawulalutho lokukha, lomgodi uyatshona; uwathethe ngaphi pho amanzi aphilayo?
\v 12 Wena umkhulu yini kulobaba wethu uJakobe, owasinika umgodi, wanatha kuwo yena, labantwana bakhe, lemihlambi yakhe?
\v 13 UJesu waphendula wathi kuye: Wonke onatha lamanzi, uzakoma futhi;
\v 14 kodwa loba ngubani onatha amanzi mina engizamnika wona, kasoze ome kuze kube laphakade\x + 6.35,51,58. 7.37.\x*; kodwa amanzi engizamnika wona azakuba ngumthombo wamanzi phakathi kwakhe ogobhozela empilweni elaphakade\x + 6.54.\x*.
\v 15 Owesifazana wathi kuye: Nkosi, ngipha lawomanzi, ukuze ngingomi, ngingabe ngiseza lapha ukukha\x + 6.34.\x*.
\v 16 UJesu wathi kuye: Hamba, ubize umkakho, uze lapha\x + 16.8.\x*.
\v 17 Owesifazana waphendula wathi: Kangilandoda. UJesu wathi kuye: Utsho kuhle ukuthi: Kangilandoda;
\v 18 ngoba usuke waba lamadoda amahlanu, le olayo khathesi kayisiyo indoda yakho; lokhu ukutsho uqinisile.
\v 19 Owesifazana wathi kuye: Nkosi, ngiyabona ukuthi wena ungumprofethi\x + 6.14.\x*.
\v 20 Obaba bethu babekhonza kulintaba\x + Hlu. 9.7. Gen. 12.6,7. 13.4. 33.18,20. Dute. 11.29. Josh. 8.33.\x*; kodwa lina lithi iseJerusalema indawo lapho okufanele umuntu akhonze khona\x + Dute. 12.5.\x*.
\v 21 UJesu wathi kuye: Mama, kholwa kimi, ukuthi ihola liyeza\x + 5.25.\x*, lapho elizakhonza uBaba\x + 4.12,20.\x* kungeyisikho kulintaba, kumbe eJerusalema\x + Mal. 1.11. 1 Tim. 2.8.\x*.
\v 22 Lina likhonza elingakwaziyo\x + 2 Kho. 17.28-34.\x*; thina sikhonza esikwaziyo; ngoba usindiso luvela kumaJuda\x + Gen. 49.10. Isa. 2.3. Roma 3.1,2. 9.4,5.\x*.
\v 23 Kodwa ihola liyeza njalo seliyilo\x + 5.25.\x*, lapho abakhonzi abaqotho bazakhonza uBaba ngomoya\x + Fil. 3.3. Juda 1.20.\x* langeqiniso\x + Hlab. 145.18.\x*; ngoba-ke uBaba udinga abanjalo abamkhonzayo\x + Luka 19.10.\x*.
\v 24 UNkulunkulu unguMoya\x + 2 Kor. 3.17.\x*; lalabo abamkhonzayo, bafanele ukukhonza ngomoya\x + Fil. 3.3. Juda 1.20.\x* langeqiniso\x + Hlab. 145.18.\x*.
\v 25 Owesifazana wathi kuye: Ngiyazi ukuthi uMesiya uyeza okuthiwa nguKristu\x + 1.41.\x*; nxa lo esefikile\x + Dute. 18.18. Joha. 4.29,39.\x*, uzasitshela konke\x + 16.13-15.\x*.
\v 26 UJesu wathi kuye: Mina nginguye, okhuluma lawe\x + 9.37. 4.42.\x*.
\p
\v 27 Kwathi ngalesosikhathi bafika abafundi bakhe, bamangala ukuthi wayekhuluma lowesifazana; kodwa kakho owathi: Udingani? Kumbe: Ukhulumelani laye?
\v 28 Ngakho owesifazana wasetshiya inkonxa yakhe, wasesuka waya emzini, wathi ebantwini:
\v 29 Wozani, libone umuntu, ongitshele konke engakwenzayo\x + 4.17,18,25.\x*; kambe kayisuye yini uKristu lo\x + Mat. 12.23. Joha. 4.33.\x*?
\v 30 Ngakho baphuma emzini, beza kuye.
\p
\v 31 Kusenjalo abafundi bamncenga besithi: \w Rabi\w**\x + 1.38.\x*, dlana\x + 4.6,8.\x*.
\v 32 Kodwa wathi kubo: Mina ngilokudla engikudlayo lina elingakwaziyo.
\v 33 Basebekhulumisana abafundi \add besithi\add*: Kambe ukhona omlethele ukudla\x + 4.11,15. 2.20. 3.4. 6.34,42,52.\x*?
\v 34 UJesu wathi kubo: Ukudla kwami\x + Jobe 23.12.\x* kuyikuthi ngenze intando yongithumileyo\x + 5.30. 6.38.\x*, lokuthi ngiqede umsebenzi wakhe\x + 5.36. 17.4. 19.30.\x*.
\v 35 Kalitsho yini ukuthi: Kuseselenyanga ezine ukuthi kufike ukuvuna? Khangelani, ngithi kini: Phakamisani amehlo enu\x + Luka 6.20.\x*, libone amasimu\x + Luka 21.21.\x*, ngoba asehle emhlophe elungele isivuno\x + Mat. 9.37. Luka 10.2. Joha. 4.40.\x*.
\v 36 Njalo ovunayo wemukela umvuzo\x + 1 Kor. 9.17,18.\x*, njalo abuthe isithelo empilweni elaphakade; ukuze bobabili ohlanyelayo\x + Mark. 4.14.\x* lovunayo bathokoze bendawonye\x + 4.38.\x*.
\v 37 Ngoba kulokhu ilizwi liqinisile elokuthi: Omunye ngohlanyelayo, lomunye ngovunayo\x + Jobe 31.8.\x*.
\v 38 Mina ngalithuma ukuvuna\x + 4.38.\x* lokho elingakusebenzelanga;\x + Josh. 24.13.\x* abanye basebenzile, lina-ke selingenile emsebenzini wabo\x + Seb. 8.5,17,25.\x*.
\p
\v 39 Njalo amaSamariya amanengi akulowomuzi akholwa kuye ngenxa yelizwi lowesifazana\x + 4.5,8.\x*, elafakaza lisithi: Ungitshele konke engikwenzileyo\x + 4.29.\x*.
\v 40 Kwathi esefikile kuye amaSamariya, amncenga ukuthi ahlale lawo\x + 1.38.\x*; wasehlala khona insuku ezimbili\x + 1.38.\x*.
\v 41 Abanengi bengezelelwa bakholwa ngenxa yelizwi lakhe.
\v 42 Basebesithi kowesifazana: Kasisakholwa ngenxa yokutsho kwakho; ngoba sesizizwele thina, siyazi ukuthi oqotho lo unguMsindisi womhlaba, uKristu\x + 1 Joha. 4.14. 1 Tim. 4.10.\x*.
\s Ukusiliswa kwendodana yenduna eKapenawume
\p
\v 43 Kwathi emva kwensuku ezimbili wasuka lapho\x + 4.40.\x*, waya eGalili\x + Mat. 4.12,13.\x*;
\v 44 ngoba uJesu ngokwakhe wafakaza ukuthi umprofethi kaladumo elizweni lakibo\x + Mat. 13.57. Joha. 4.1,3.\x*.
\v 45 Wathi esefikile eGalili, amaGalili amemukela\x + Luka 9.53.\x*, ebonile konke akwenzayo eJerusalema emkhosini\x + 2.23. 3.2.\x*; ngoba lawo ayeyile emkhosini\x + Dute. 16.16.\x*.
\p
\v 46 UJesu wafika-ke futhi eKana yeGalili\x + 2.1.\x*, lapho enza khona amanzi \add aba\add* liwayini\x + 2.9.\x*. Kwakukhona othile owesikhosini, ondodana yakhe yayigula eKapenawume\x + Luka 4.23.\x*.
\v 47 Esezwile ukuthi uJesu u\add se\add*fikile eGalili evela eJudiya\x + 4.3.\x*, waya kuye, wamncenga ukuthi ehle, asilise indodana yakhe\x + 2.12. 4.49,51. 4.46.\x*, ngoba yayisizaphela.
\v 48 Ngakho uJesu wathi kuye: Ngaphandle kokuthi\x + Mat. 12.38. Joha. 4.42,44. 12.37.\x* libone izibonakaliso\x + Mat. 24.24. Mark. 13.22. Seb. 4.30. 5.12. 14.3. 15.12. Roma 15.19. 2 Kor. 12.12. Heb. 2.4. Joha. 20.30. Seb. 2.19,22,43. 6.8. 7.36. 2 Thes. 2.9.\x* lezimangaliso\x + Mat. 24.24. Mark. 13.22. Seb. 4.30. 5.12. 14.3. 15.12. Roma 15.19. 2 Kor. 12.12. Heb. 2.4. Joha. 20.30. Seb. 2.19,22,43. 6.8. 7.36. 2 Thes. 2.9.\x*, kalisoze likholwe.
\v 49 Owesikhosini wathi kuye: Nkosi, yehla\x + 2.12. 4.49,51. 4.46.\x* engakafi umntanami\x + Mark. 5.35. Luka 8.49. Joha. 11.21,22,32.\x*.
\v 50 UJesu wathi kuye: Hamba; indodana yakho iyaphila. Umuntu wasekholwa ilizwi uJesu alikhuluma laye, wasuka wahamba.
\v 51 Kwathi esesehla\x + 2.12. 4.49,51. 4.46.\x*, inceku zakhe zamhlangabeza, zabika zathi: Umntanakho uyaphila.
\v 52 Wasezibuza ihola aqale ngalo ukuba ngcono. Zasezisithi kuye: Izolo ngehola lesikhombisa uqhuqho lumyekele\x + 1.39.\x*.
\v 53 Ngakho uyise wazi ukuthi \add kwaku\add*ngalelohola uJesu athi ngalo kuye: Indodana yakho iyaphila; wasekholwa yena lendlu yakhe yonke.
\v 54 UJesu waphinda wakwenza lokhu kwaba yisibonakaliso sesibili\x + 2.11. 4.45,46.\x*, efikile eGalili evela eJudiya\x + 4.3.\x*.